522
00:35:07,958 --> 00:35:09,500
- Hi.
- Get in.

523
00:35:09,583 --> 00:35:10,541
Okay, fine.

524
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:16,083
Sorry, I was expecting
Jeff the photographer.

525
00:35:18,625 --> 00:35:20,416
-He'll get over it.
