656
00:45:33,666 --> 00:45:34,625
Oh!

657
00:45:34,708 --> 00:45:37,166
That's somethin'
to be proud of, hey?

658
00:45:39,458 --> 00:45:41,458
Yeah, we did good, Frankie.

659
00:45:53,666 --> 00:45:54,625
Oi.

660
00:45:55,791 --> 00:45:56,625
Yeah.

661
00:45:58,875 --> 00:45:59,750
Piece of cake.

662
00:46:07,041 --> 00:46:08,041
Ah…

