00:46:16,500 --> 00:46:17,875
♪ You know you can't fool me ♪

664
00:46:19,083 --> 00:46:23,291
♪ I've been lovin' you too long ♪

665
00:46:24,541 --> 00:46:25,791
♪ It started s-- ♪

