717
00:56:47,666 --> 00:56:48,500
I dunno.

718
00:56:48,583 --> 00:56:51,458
Oh, fuck, we're in so much shit.

719
00:57:17,458 --> 00:57:18,458
Ooh!

720
00:57:19,833 --> 00:57:20,666
Okay.

721
00:57:21,833 --> 00:57:22,666
We're good.

722
00:57:24,458 --> 00:57:26,750
